sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Caller
    participant API as Public API
    participant Application as Lifecycle + Application
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline + Delegation
    participant Facades as Facade Stack
    participant Core as Rules + Remainder

    Note over API,Core: Default warm single-value path. Factories, caches, visitors, and most decorators are collapsed

    Caller->>API: fizzBuzzValue(n)
    API->>Application: orchestrateSingleValueResolution(n, innerResolver)
    activate Application
    Application->>Application: transition to COMPUTING
    Application->>Application: execute PRE_COMPUTE handler chain
    Application->>Application: CommandInvoker → ValueCommand → SessionFacade
    Application->>Application: ServiceActivator → Dispatcher → ServiceEndpoint
    Application->>Pipeline: executeSingleValuePipeline(n)
    activate Pipeline
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: resolve manager → select execution command
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: DelegationOrchestrator → BusinessDelegate
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: governance → PublicApiDelegate → request adapter
    Pipeline->>Facades: resolveValue(n)
    activate Facades
    Note over Facades: Validation, interception, configuration, document, AOP, transaction, security, proxy, bridge, and normalization layers
    Facades->>Core: execute decorated expression-tree command
    activate Core
    loop Rules in priority order: FizzBuzz, Fizz, Buzz
        Core->>Core: interpret DivisibleBy expression
        Core->>Core: supervisor → locator → delegation service
        Core->>Core: chain → strategy → 7-layer protocol stack
        Core->>Core: terminal native n % divisor
    end
    Core-->>Facades: raw output label or number
    deactivate Core
    Facades->>Facades: normalize and post-process result
    Facades-->>Pipeline: result
    deactivate Facades
    Pipeline-->>Application: endpoint response.computedResult
    deactivate Pipeline
    Application->>Application: validate result
    Application->>Application: execute POST_COMPUTE handler chain
    Application->>Application: transition to FORMATTED
    Application-->>API: formattedResult
    deactivate Application
    API-->>Caller: Fizz / Buzz / FizzBuzz / number
